We have recommended that the Management:

Require additional payment for the uncollected penalties during the CY 2019.


Require the submission of certified copy of Annual Income Tax Return to Business Taxpayers on the second quarter of the year;

Adjust the business tax and;

Collect the difference if there are discrepancies between the amount appearing in the ITR and gross sales declared in the business tax application form.

